24#include <sys/cdefs.h>
25__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_gr_ctxgk20a.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:32 riastradh Exp $");
26
27#include "ctxgf100.h"
28#include "gf100.h"
29
30#include <subdev/mc.h>
31
32static void
33gk20a_grctx_generate_main(struct gf100_gr *gr, struct gf100_grctx *info)
34{
35 struct nvkm_device *device = gr->base.engine.subdev.device;
36 const struct gf100_grctx_func *grctx = gr->func->grctx;
37 int idle_timeout_save;
38 int i;
39
40 gf100_gr_mmio(gr, gr->fuc_sw_ctx);
41
42 gf100_gr_wait_idle(gr);
43
44 idle_timeout_save = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x404154);
45 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404154, 0x00000000);
46
47 grctx->attrib(info);
48
49 grctx->unkn(gr);
50
51 gf100_grctx_generate_tpcid(gr);
52 gf100_grctx_generate_r406028(gr);
53 gk104_grctx_generate_r418bb8(gr);
54 gf100_grctx_generate_r406800(gr);
55
56 for (i = 0; i < 8; i++)
57 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x4064d0 + (i * 0x04), 0x00000000);
58
59 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x405b00, (gr->tpc_total << 8) | gr->gpc_nr);
60
61 gk104_grctx_generate_rop_active_fbps(gr);
62
63 nvkm_mask(device, 0x5044b0, 0x8000000, 0x8000000);
64
65 gf100_gr_wait_idle(gr);
66
67 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404154, idle_timeout_save);
68 gf100_gr_wait_idle(gr);
69
70 gf100_gr_mthd(gr, gr->fuc_method);
71 gf100_gr_wait_idle(gr);
72
73 gf100_gr_icmd(gr, gr->fuc_bundle);
74 grctx->pagepool(info);
75 grctx->bundle(info);
76}
77
78const struct gf100_grctx_func
79gk20a_grctx = {
80 .main = gk20a_grctx_generate_main,
81 .unkn = gk104_grctx_generate_unkn,
82 .bundle = gk104_grctx_generate_bundle,
83 .bundle_size = 0x1800,
84 .bundle_min_gpm_fifo_depth = 0x62,
85 .bundle_token_limit = 0x100,
86 .pagepool = gk104_grctx_generate_pagepool,
87 .pagepool_size = 0x8000,
88 .attrib = gf117_grctx_generate_attrib,
89 .attrib_nr_max = 0x240,
90 .attrib_nr = 0x240,
91 .alpha_nr_max = 0x648 + (0x648 / 2),
92 .alpha_nr = 0x648,
93};
